{"tid":745892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【為老不尊】葵涌七歲女童遭非禮　警拘六旬翁","createTime":"2018-07-17T06:55:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T11:12:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"72546ec56e2cd2f09f3eb3d03198c07ff3e03bf6","tid":745892,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:55:11.000Z","msg":"昨日(16日)晚上9時許，警方接獲一名28歲婦人報案，指其7歲女兒於葵涌上角街遭人非禮。警方接報到場經初步調查，案件暫列「非禮」，並以涉嫌非禮罪名，當場拘捕一名60歲姓吳老翁，案件交由葵青警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/211469/%E7%82%BA%E8%80%81%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%8A-%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E4%B8%83%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5%E9%81%AD%E9%9D%9E%E7%A6%AE-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E7%BF%81?utm_campaign=yahooexchange2018&amp;utm_source=relatedlink&amp;utm_medium=referral\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F211469%2F%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B0%258A-%25E8%2591%25B5%25E6%25B6%258C%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%259D%259E%25E7%25A6%25AE-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%2598%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%2597%25AC%25E7%25BF%2581%3Futm_campaign%3Dyahooexchange2018%26utm_source%3Drelatedlink%26utm_medium%3Dreferral&d=ibPqBhc%2FNkKTCLocaVvfiNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=61faa9a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/211469/%E7%82%BA%E8%80%81%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%8A-%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E4%B8%83%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5%E9%81%AD%E9%9D%9E%E7%A6%AE-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E7%BF%81?utm_campaign=yahooexchange2018&amp;utm_source=relatedlink&amp;utm_medium=referral</a>"},{"pid":"08c1b8cf7e29ab66168125b3c1c17862985ca2df","tid":745892,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:57:33.000Z","msg":"有啲廢中廢老好仆街<br />\n會恰鳩啲細嘅唔出聲 然後抽水視姦哄埋去"},{"pid":"b40f1c319152f2ab8dd7046d46e335c26c991ebd","tid":745892,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11: